e":{"pid":"99a29a6b9aa98fb3970847c137d3ef835efe1891","tid":1302552,"uid":243883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:28:06.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n大家出到嚟嘅唔好忘記仲有海富中心嘅陳伯伯同其他絕食者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c613c459a0547cb1660b120c824e207108d60ce","tid":1302552,"uid":88175,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c94c463645fc712988355596c6c9fdfbc25da406","tid":1302552,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:50:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab352bc7e2f404eb26ae428b50b9fe0414790c0a","tid":1302552,"uid":277666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88fe60ee15a2cf021b7904a2a62770940b38bc78","tid":1302552,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:51:20.000Z","msg":"要人呀 快啲黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1215ae5629f0c0461058562463a4f0659d8e7d","tid":1302552,"uid":47647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T11:53:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a961fedb9673759b4aba1a6b4b7675d85f8dff66","tid":1302552,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:03:14.000Z","msg":"去緊"},{"pid":"2a0ba6675fb15631e44c352fc8669a432ab8cba6","tid":1302552,"uid":124140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:08:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddea6fd5c0f144920aee38f6c2fba1a714927085","tid":1302552,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:18:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190710/59809521\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190710%2F59809521&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=10dbea7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190710%2F59809521&h=01bd0617\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190710/59809521</a><br />\n <br />\n【逆權運動】開朗妙齡女反送中輕生 好友詫異：可想而知有幾絕望<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即時要聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190710/large/1562760291_c5b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190710%2Flarge%2F1562760291_c5b6.png&h=7b2ac7c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《蘋果》製圖、原圖由黎樹雄攝<br />\n<br />\n因「反送中」而輕生的28歲麥小姐，民間今晚於中環愛丁堡廣場為她舉行追思會，其好友翁小姐接受訪問時表示，麥小姐生前為人開朗，從未有異樣，6月時積極參與反送中運動，沒料到上周三（3日）卻選擇離開。對於好友離世，除傷感外，麥小姐認為，也提醒大家要持續關心身邊戰友，「但最緊要都係政府回應番市民訴求，因為對於個社會已經造成深層次傷害，只要一日唔回應，傷痛一日都喺度。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【逆權運動】沒普選不會有民主自由 黎智英︰六四悲劇可能在香港重演<br />\n<br />\n回憶起麥小姐生前的點滴，翁小姐表示，她們已相識近15年，直到大學以後，兩人幾乎每日都會聯絡，「佢係一個好開心嘅人，完全估唔到佢會用咁嘅方式去離開。」翁小姐指，過去麥小姐不算是遊行示威的常客，但自6月後，幾乎每場遊行集會都有參與，「我哋雖然係分開各自參與，但每一次都會text大家，去confirm係咪安全。」<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n回想整個6月，翁小姐直言不察覺麥小姐有何異樣，「只係同佢傾計嗰陣，佢會repeat好多次心很累，但嗰期大家都心很累&hellip;&hellip;」翁小姐記得，最後一次與麥小姐互通訊息，是7.1早上，「嗰時佢好早就出咗去金鐘，仲send咗張相，話畀我聽佢位置喺邊」，只是沒料到這是她此生最後一次和麥小姐通訊，「如果我之後嗰日有搵佢，會唔會一切就唔同？」念及此處，翁小姐不免自責。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【逆權運動】在美港人發動去信行動 促國會盡早通過香港法案<br />\n<br />\n好友離世，其中一封信留了給她，「我當時handle唔到自己情緒，喺地鐵站喊咗成個鐘，先去拎封信，但當時已經sense到佢嘅離開，同政治有關。」後來。翁小姐與其他共同朋友商討後，得到麥小姐家人同意，把其遺言公開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於接二連三有人間接或直接因「反送中」而輕生，翁小姐直言「睇唔透」，也坦言不會判斷對與錯，「但都唔鼓勵」。對於身邊的戰友，翁小姐明言「一個都不能少」，認為身旁的人需多加關心，但坦言即使再多的陪伴，有時也難解社會上已造成的深層次傷害，「其實我無諗過連佢咁樣嘅人都會離開，可想而知有幾絕望，政府一日唔回應訴求，個傷痛一日都會喺度。」<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【每周送10萬】<br />\n升級壹會員獨家尊享，立即參加10萬火急大抽獎 !<br />\n*推廣生意的競賽牌照號碼：52302-9"},{"pid":"296230b8011bc20661f8f8322894013cb5302fed","tid":1302552,"uid":267887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ede7b65f5ba21e80b97b9ee70dd0fc09a44a3c5","tid":1302552,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:20:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da1cc665cc9e50ad5207b197a7f5f378e1baced7","tid":1302552,"uid":219276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"有無手足知道呢個鐘數仲有邊度有花買?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9267039f61c1390feccc943a34100dbcda7d5c10","tid":1302552,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:24:17.000Z","msg":"中環站k出口最近， 向住大會堂方向行就得"},{"pid":"1783408da06fc65865a176429311f541bef84f85","tid":1302552,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:24:44.000Z","msg":"一千人"},{"pid":"d62a0a2d3cf988abfb052b71356b70f4c3ce2337","tid":1302552,"uid":10973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da1cc665cc9e50ad5207b197a7f5f378e1baced7","tid":1302552,"uid":219276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"有無手足知道呢個鐘數仲有邊度有花買?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T12:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/241bLmC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F241bLmC.jpg&h=755e0960&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28bb0ac2abc62228f4a846852f65aad9a76a7f0b","tid":1302552,"uid":219276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d62a0a2d3cf988abfb052b71356b70f4c3ce2337","tid":1302552,"uid":10973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da1cc665cc9e50ad5207b197a7f5f378e1baced7","tid":1302552,"uid"